description: New or Struggling Entrepreneur? Need business clarity? Looking for a career change? Or do you just want to get more familiar with your soul. My 7 step cosmic mapping program will show you EXACTLY what your cosmic business purpose is so you can manifest your ideas, increase your business confidence and get on the right track. No matter how long you have been on the journey towards success, if you are struggling to pull your business together this program is for you. I have outlined every step towards clarity of your business purpose in detail, and it is all related to your personal birth chart so you can get your own unique instructions and start applying them to your business right away to get the results you have been trying to get for a long time.
title: 7 Steps to Mapping (M.A.P) Your Career Using Astrology
